description:
This song is from the game Eternal Senia.  I originally tried to create here on Musescore, but it was horrendous, so I remade it!  I also heard that for some reason the mobile version of Musescore changed my tempo, which was different compared to the PC version, so hopefully I fixed that to.

I couldn't find any sheet music for this song, so I had to play it all by ear.
Overall, just enjoy the song, and tell me how I did!

Note: I do not own the rights to this song, the game, or anything else related to this.
title: The Other Side of Sorrow
